{"id": 2072, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于在社交网络里怎么运用标点符号，你都有啥心得？", "description": "最能代表我本人气质的标点应该是句号：leave me alone。", "record_count": 2149, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171218174330Nohz35ZnVsfw0xKu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 256000, "content": "自从当了语文老师，尽量在社交网络中都注意标点符号的运用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065518}, {"id": 256001, "content": "……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 587852}, {"id": 257025, "content": "句号从不会单独出现，只会“。。。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224390}, {"id": 256002, "content": "不经常用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220532}, {"id": 256258, "content": "能换行就不打标点了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 256003, "content": "。。。说明不想说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220538}, {"id": 256004, "content": "。和n个句号（n>=2)有着实质性的区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220544}, {"id": 256260, "content": "情绪很激动的时候表达方式就会变成：\n我$&@€£*%#!!!!!!!!!\n(ㅍ_ㅍ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316685}, {"id": 256005, "content": "？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187991}, {"id": 256006, "content": "....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141879}, {"id": 256007, "content": "啊、如果要用到引号的话一般会用「」表示强调或者引用之类的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220563}, {"id": 256008, "content": "。加了会比较严肃，有时候还会有我们完了的意思。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 256009, "content": "句末用括号（）把自己真正想表达的意思言简意赅的说出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 256010, "content": "男生常用～不是死基就是死宅", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 256011, "content": "…和……代表情绪和语境明显不同的两种意思，具体应用请看《不同长度的省略号词典》一书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 256012, "content": "一本正经地胡说八道用“。”号。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 256013, "content": "其实很少用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208695}, {"id": 256014, "content": "...可以表示很多意思，再加上语气词就更多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174603}, {"id": 256015, "content": "用。。。缓冲语气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289754}, {"id": 256016, "content": "要用来做表情啦(๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195734}, {"id": 258320, "content": "emmmm 嗯 嗯嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151928}, {"id": 256017, "content": "？？？？？？？？？？？？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871628}, {"id": 256018, "content": "我喜欢\n这样的运用\n_\n在朋友圈里\n他们说是\n我的专属风格\n/\n转行 + _\n例如：\n\n我喜欢\n对一堵墙说话\n世界上只有它\n不会反驳我\n_", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130091}, {"id": 257298, "content": "空格代替，。      ！？无限长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121755}, {"id": 256019, "content": "爱你么么哒～(^з^)-☆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020124}, {"id": 256020, "content": "好的呢、", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220586}, {"id": 256021, "content": "只有我喜欢用“、”吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220586}, {"id": 256022, "content": "呵跟呵呵跟呵呵呵呵呵呵的区别?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220596}, {"id": 256023, "content": "你们都是天选之子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808042}, {"id": 261144, "content": "几百年前习惯不带标点 像现在一样 只会用空格 要不然很fzl", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330251}, {"id": 255769, "content": "一串句号搞定所有。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147468}, {"id": 256025, "content": "这东西难道不是用来组成颜文字的么？@_@", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213870}, {"id": 255770, "content": "！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182814}, {"id": 255771, "content": "工科男表示基本是句号  句号的长短就很能表明情绪了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209439}, {"id": 256027, "content": "空格代表逗号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211477}, {"id": 258587, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233850}, {"id": 255772, "content": "尽量不要用句号", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217875}, {"id": 255773, "content": "不用标点，打一句话发出去再打一句话，俗称刷屏式", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186035}, {"id": 256029, "content": "标点符号是最长久的表情包(>﹏<)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215763}, {"id": 255774, "content": "......", "image": null, "praise_count": 358, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540018}, {"id": 255776, "content": "我不用", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219806}, {"id": 256032, "content": "：)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94349}, {"id": 255777, "content": "～ 和长辈老师说话必备 做小伏低。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253313}, {"id": 256033, "content": "我牛不牛逼我不知道，但是当别人跟我说“你死了地球照样转的时候”，我听着就觉得地球在硬撑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930612}, {"id": 256035, "content": "用句号看着很正式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102211}, {"id": 257059, "content": "#無窮無盡的個人獨白還自以為很有性格殊不知這個符號根本不是這種用法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210106}, {"id": 257060, "content": "？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790711}, {"id": 257316, "content": "喜欢用？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225706}, {"id": 255781, "content": "要么。。。要么来个表情，没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 256037, "content": "不知道平时怎么用标点的。\n好像没有什么特别的习惯，一般都还是严谨的按照语法使用标点，就像现在这样。\n聊天时候标点符号用得乱七八糟的和句子切得很碎的，给人一种没文化的感觉。如果是女人就会联想到胸大无脑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822743}]}